short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Are you a basketball fan? Flappy Dunk let you throw the basketball into the hoop to start scoring as much as you can.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Create your high scores. Launch this cool basketball dunk game. Users must pass the basketball through as many rings as they can in the popular game flappy basketball.


How to Play
With the aid of the mouse, you must pass the ball through the basketball hoop. If the ball goes off the platform or you skip the rings in the flappy basketball game, which requires incredibly precise timing, you will lose.

Features of the Flappy Basketball game include simple controls, vibrant visuals, amusing noises, and an endless level.
